# Failure-Mode Graph — {{ project.name }}

This document contains the Failure-Mode Graph (G) for {{ project.name }}: the mapping of
stress-test → breakpoint relations discovered during AEE stress-testing.

Failure modes are not defects — they are **recovery opportunities**. Each mode has a
recovery hint and a corresponding `RecoveryProposal` emitted by `RecoveryOperator`.

Review with `specsmith audit` after requirements or tests change.

